title: adidas Skateboarding Paris Feature
description:
Paris campaign shoot in July 2007 with Dennis Busenitz, Tim O'Connor, Benny Fairfax, Dave Bachinsky, Nestor Judkins and Lem Villemin with a special appearance by Mark Gonzales in New York City.
 Official Website: http://www.adidas.com/skateboarding
